OL,4,Cfor better future for NI
OL,6,FStormont's first nationalist first
OL,7,Fminister Michelle O'Neill has pledged
OL,8,Fto work with unionists to build a
OL,9,Fbetter future for Northern Ireland.
OL,11,Fprovided a moment of history on the
OL,12,Fday the powersharing institutions
OL,13,Freturned after a two-year hiatus.
