OL,6,FThe two top jobs in the ministerial
OL,7,Fexecutive wield equal power and
OL,8,Fresponsibility, but the elevation of a
OL,9,Frepublican to the office of first
OL,10,Fminister, by virtue of Sinn Fein
OL,11,Fbecoming the region's largest
OL,12,Fpolitical party in the 2022 Assembly
OL,13,Felection, is undoubtedly a significant
OL,14,Fsymbolic moment for Northern Ireland.
OL,16,FThe sitting started with the election
OL,17,Fof former DUP leader Edwin Poots as
OL,18,Fspeaker, a move which allowed the rest
OL,19,Fof the business to proceed.
