OL,6,FFollowing the nomination of Ms O'Neill
OL,7,Fand Ms Little-Pengelly, Alliance
OL,8,Fleader Naomi Long was confirmed as
OL,9,Freturning to serve as justice minister.
OL,11,FThe remaining ministerial portfolios
OL,12,Fwere decided by the D'Hondt process
OL,13,Fbased on party strengths.
