OL,6,F"As First Minister I am wholeheartedly
OL,7,Fcommitted to continuing the work of
OL,8,Freconciliation between all of our
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,F"The past cannot be changed or undone.
OL,13,F"But what we can do is build a better
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,F"I will never ask anyone to 'move on',
OL,17,Fbut I do hope that we can 'move
OL,18,Fforward'. I want us to walk in harmony
