OL,3,CFirst minister O'Neill pledges to work
OL,4,Cfor better future for NI
OL,6,F"Let us prove that difference is
OL,7,Fsomething that can be a strength
OL,8,Fthrough recognition and respect. That
OL,9,Fdifference need not be a barrier to
OL,10,Fprogress and delivering.
OL,12,F"This is my pledge. I love this place
OL,13,Fwe call home. I will work tirelessly
OL,14,Ffor delivery for all the people of
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland from every
OL,16,Fbackground. I will do so with the best
OL,17,Fof my abilities honoured by the
OL,18,Fprivilege and opportunity to do so.
OL,20,F"Let's do it side by side and let's
OL,21,Fkeep Northern Ireland moving forward."
